393
00:27:00,950 --> 00:27:02,080
在你们的竞选团队里
On your campaign?

394
00:27:02,900 --> 00:27:03,880
是的  很讽刺
Yeah, it's ironic...

395
00:27:03,880 --> 00:27:06,810
我得挂了  祝你好运
I'm gonna hang up now. Good luck.

396
00:27:07,140 --> 00:27:09,310
但我觉得她是搞砸了
...but I think she may have just tanked it.

397
