总统先生  移植手术完毕
Mr. President... the transplant's complete.

398
00:27:15,090 --> 00:27:16,520
他们正在缝合刀口
Now they're closing him up.

399
00:27:17,240 --> 00:27:19,150
接下来就看他能否适应新器官了
We'll see how he accepts the new organ.

400
00:27:21,370 --> 00:27:23,740
也许我们该给克莱尔打个电话了
Maybe we should try and get Claire on the phone.

401
00:27:24,140 --> 00:27:24,990
嗯
Yeah.

402
00:27:25,770 --> 00:27:28,180
快了  我们在等他
Soon. We're waiting for him now.

403
00:27:30,470 --> 00:27:33,410
好的  好  谢谢  唐纳德
Okay. Okay, thank you, Donald.

404
00:27:35,190 --> 00:27:38,800
-挺顺利喽  -除非他的身体排斥这个肝脏
- So it's going well? - Well, unless his body rejects the liver.

405
00:27:42,590 --> 00:27:44,750
-总统先生  -安德伍德夫人
- Mr. President. - Mrs. Underwood.

406
00:27:45,760 --> 00:27:47,210
总统先生
Mr. President.

407
