我以为我们要单独见面
I thought we were meeting alone.

408
00:27:50,960 --> 00:27:53,490
作为政府的代表
As the administration's representative,

409
00:27:53,520 --> 00:27:56,170
我需要参与到所有谈话中
I need to participate in any conversations--

410
00:27:56,170 --> 00:28:00,060
国务卿女士  我相信我的人说得很清楚了
Madam Secretary, I believe my people were very clear, hmm?

411
00:28:01,010 --> 00:28:03,350
能给我们点时间吗  凯茜
Would you give us a moment, please, Cathy?

412
00:28:04,690 --> 00:28:05,900
一小会儿就好
Just a little while.

413
00:28:12,290 --> 00:28:13,700
我就在外面
I'll be outside.

414
00:28:20,420 --> 00:28:23,490
手术进展怎么样
So... how is surgery going?

415
00:28:24,130 --> 00:28:25,110
目前还好
So far, so good.

416
00:28:25,110 --> 00:28:28,730
你一定累坏了  快坐吧  坐吧
Ah, you must be exhausted. Now, sit. Sit.

417
00:28:30,500 --> 00:28:33,370
你一定更想在医院里吧
I imagine you'd rather be at the hospital.

418
00:28:33,420 --> 00:28:34,830
这事太重要了
Well, this is too important,

419
00:28:34,830 --> 00:28:37,980
您又不肯跟杜兰特国务卿谈判
and you weren't going to negotiate with Secretary Durant.

420
00:28:37,980 --> 00:28:40,470
