Oh, well, isn't that why we're sitting here?

422
00:28:44,580 --> 00:28:48,370
也许我只是想...再看到你的脸
Maybe I just wanted to... see your face again.

423
00:28:49,080 --> 00:28:50,340
也许我喜欢你这张脸
Maybe I'm fond of it.

424
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:54,440
你是个美丽的女人  安德伍德夫人
You are a beautiful woman, Mrs. Underwood, hmm?

425
00:28:55,250 --> 00:28:56,510
那双唇
Those lips...

426
00:28:59,270 --> 00:29:01,680
你能为我说句话吗
Would you say something for me?

427
00:29:04,940 --> 00:29:06,380
你可以说...
Would you say, um...

428
00:29:08,360 --> 00:29:12,210
"你真可耻  总统先生"吗
"Shame on you... Mr. President."

429
00:29:13,690 --> 00:29:16,790
当真吗  维克多  要重提那段不快吗
Really, Viktor? Are we gonna dredge that up?

430
00:29:17,900 --> 00:29:19,510
道个歉就行
