433
00:29:29,210 --> 00:29:30,150
没错
Yes.

434
00:29:32,360 --> 00:29:33,740
这倒是
Yes, this is true.

435
00:29:36,450 --> 00:29:39,080
我不是来旅游的  维克多
I'm not here for a sightseeing trip, Viktor.

436
00:29:39,890 --> 00:29:44,290
弗兰西斯需要一个肝脏  我需要救市
So, Francis needs a liver and I need a bailout.

437
00:29:45,180 --> 00:29:47,980
-你需要什么  -我需要你同意那些条款
- What do you need? - I need for you to agree to the terms.

438
00:29:47,990 --> 00:29:51,230
对啊  条款  没错
Oh, yes, the terms. The terms, yes.

439
00:29:51,410 --> 00:29:55,710
但你为什么在这儿  而不是陪着弗兰西斯
But why are you here... and not with Francis?

440
00:29:58,400 --> 00:30:00,550
你母亲生病时  你回到了她身边
When your mother is sick, you go to her.

441
00:30:01,080 --> 00:30:03,010
现在却不在你丈夫身边
Not your husband, hmm?

442
00:30:05,210 --> 00:30:06,870
那些报道是真的吗
Were the stories true?

443
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:11,110
出问题了吗  克莱尔
Are there problems, Claire?

444
00:30:12,930 --> 00:30:15,630
你对中国的顾虑是什么
What are your concerns with the Chinese?

445
00:30:18,760 --> 00:30:22,270
有太多钻井在敏感地区
There are too many drilling sites in sensitive areas.

446
00:30:22,270 --> 00:30:23,950
对我们是个安全问题
It's a security issue to us.

447
00:30:23,950 --> 00:30:25,800
你们具体担心的是哪几个钻井
And what sites, in particular, are you worried about?

448
00:30:25,800 --> 00:30:28,580
你熟悉各个区域吗
Oh, you... you are familiar with the individual zones?

449
00:30:28,590 --> 00:30:31,070
这是我的计划  我完全清楚
It's my plan. I know it backwards and forwards.

450
00:30:31,070 --> 00:30:34,990
这样啊  怪不得对你这么重要
I see, so that's why it's so important to you.

451
00:30:36,060 --> 00:30:37,700
因为这是你的
Because it's yours.

452
00:30:42,710 --> 00:30:43,970
是其中之一吗
Is it one of these?

453
00:30:45,120 --> 00:30:46,770
在太平洋海岸上
On the Pacific coast?

454
00:30:56,980 --> 00:30:58,320
您找我  先生
