455
00:31:20,250 --> 00:31:23,280
我想尽快离开这里
I wanna get out of this place as soon as possible.

456
00:31:24,940 --> 00:31:26,370
我会尽力的  先生
I'll make sure of it, sir.

457
00:31:27,840 --> 00:31:29,060
克莱尔在哪
Where's Claire?

458
00:31:30,260 --> 00:31:31,570
她在德国
She's in Germany.

459
00:31:32,610 --> 00:31:33,630
德国
Germany?

460
00:31:35,200 --> 00:31:37,160
我很多事要向您汇报  总统先生
A lot to catch you up on, Mr. President.

461
00:31:48,490 --> 00:31:51,110
-雷蒙德  -中国人开始担心了
- Raymond. - The Chinese are getting skittish.

462
00:31:51,280 --> 00:31:53,710
他们想知道为什么这么慢
They wanna know why it's taking so long.

463
00:31:53,720 --> 00:31:56,680
如果佩特罗夫不尽快同意  他们可能会退出
Now, if Petrov doesn't agree soon, they may back out.

464
00:31:56,680 --> 00:31:59,440
-谢谢  雷蒙德  -我随时待命
- Thank you, Raymond. - I'm on standby.

465
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:03,090
我们得马上达成协议
We need to shake hands on this.

466
00:32:03,090 --> 00:32:07,660
不行  我告诉过你了  库页岛上不能有
No. No, I told you, nothing on Sakhalin Island.

467
00:32:09,070 --> 00:32:11,930
只要南端两个区  你就可以救市了
It's two zones on the southern end. Then you have your bailout.

468
00:32:11,930 --> 00:32:13,950
这样会打开一扇我不想开的门
It opens a door I don't want to open.

469
00:32:14,000 --> 00:32:16,390
他们的要求很合理了  总统先生
They're being more than reasonable, Mr. President.

470
00:32:16,390 --> 00:32:18,360
合理  谁说的
Reasonable? In whose eyes?

471
00:32:18,360 --> 00:32:20,350
你们和中国在掠夺西伯利亚
You and China are raping Siberia.

472
00:32:20,350 --> 00:32:22,670
不是我们把你们的经济搞砸的
We didn't run your economy into the ground.

473
00:32:22,670 --> 00:32:23,650
是你自己
You did.

474
00:32:24,210 --> 00:32:26,660
迈克尔·科里根上吊前
Is this how you tried to convince Michael Corrigan 

475
00:32:26,660 --> 00:32:27,780
你就是这么劝他的吗
before he hung himself?

476
00:32:27,780 --> 00:32:29,840
因为你现在就是在要求我这么做
Because that's what you are asking me to do,

477
00:32:29,840 --> 00:32:31,900
在我自己的脖子上系个绳套
to tie the noose around my own neck.

478
00:32:32,730 --> 00:32:36,170
接下来呢  黑海吗  北极吗
What's next? The Black Sea? The Arctic?

479
00:32:36,180 --> 00:32:38,820
我不能允许中国船只
I cannot allow the Chinese ships 

480
00:32:38,820 --> 00:32:41,330
这么靠近我的领土
to come this close to my sovereign--

481
00:32:43,550 --> 00:32:46,620
安德伍德夫人  安德伍德总统打来找您
Mrs. Underwood, President Underwood is on the line.

482
00:32:47,580 --> 00:32:49,960
-他醒了吗  -是的  夫人
- He's awake? - Yes, ma'am.

483
00:32:51,240 --> 00:32:53,210
去吧  我们谈完了
Go, go. We're done here.

484
00:32:58,740 --> 00:33:01,430
-我现在没空跟他通话  -安德伍德夫人
- I can't speak with him right now. - Mrs. Underwood--

485
00:33:01,430 --> 00:33:03,550
我有空时会告诉你的
I will let you know when I'm available.

486
00:33:03,970 --> 00:33:04,880
是  夫人
Yes, ma'am.

487
00:33:08,050 --> 00:33:10,250
你应该跟你丈夫谈谈
You should talk to your husband.

488
00:33:10,990 --> 00:33:13,270
不达成协议  我不会离开这里的
I'm not leaving here until we have an agreement.

489
00:33:13,280 --> 00:33:15,000
但你是个业余选手  克莱尔
But you're an amateur, Claire.

490
00:33:15,000 --> 00:33:17,710
你飞过来  挺起胸脯
You fly in, you puff up your chest 

491
00:33:17,710 --> 00:33:19,800
假装自己是总统
and you pretend to play president.

492
00:33:19,800 --> 00:33:21,950
但没了你丈夫  你又算什么呢
But what would you be without your husband?

493
00:33:21,950 --> 00:33:24,410
什么也不是  只是张漂亮脸蛋
Nothing. A pretty face.

494
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:30,490
那好吧  你想演总统就演吧
So, yes, play the president if you like.

495
00:33:30,490 --> 00:33:35,370
去吧  告诉中国人他们在太平洋上什么也得不到
Go. Tell the Chinese they get nothing on the Pacific.

496
00:33:35,830 --> 00:33:39,850
你觉得你做得到吗  安德伍德夫人
You think you can do that, Mrs. Underwood?

497
00:33:41,480 --> 00:33:43,020
你的人民正在受苦
Your people are hurting.

498
00:33:43,890 --> 00:33:46,990
最多六个月  他们就会去红场游行
Six months at most, they're gonna be marching on Red Square.

499
00:33:47,950 --> 00:33:50,800
我不想再给你留面子了
I'm done letting you have your dignity.

500
00:33:51,060 --> 00:33:53,990
事实上  你就是个跪着的乞丐
The truth is you're a beggar on your knees,

501
00:33:53,990 --> 00:33:57,940
我们逼你吃什么  你就得吃什么
and you will take whatever we shove down your throat.

502
00:34:06,690 --> 00:34:07,670
维克多
Viktor.

503
00:34:12,080 --> 00:34:15,260
接受协议  挽回面子
Take the deal. Get your dignity back.

504
00:34:28,700 --> 00:34:29,940
国务卿女士
Madam Secretary.

505
00:34:39,720 --> 00:34:42,810
61和67区联合控制权
Joint control of zones 61 and 67.

506
00:34:44,580 --> 00:34:47,910
我们已取得协议  只等总统同意 
We've got an agreement, pending the president's approval.

507
00:34:48,720 --> 00:34:50,320
他在睡觉了
Well, he's sleeping now.

508
00:34:51,680 --> 00:34:54,260
他们即将把他转移回白宫
They're moving him back to the White House soon.

509
00:34:54,260 --> 00:34:57,010
-他看起来怎么样  -我只简单跟他聊了几句
- And how did he seem? - I only talked to him briefly,

510
00:34:57,080 --> 00:35:01,690
但是医生说器官...目前情况良好
but the doctors say the organ is... taking well so far.

511
00:35:02,110 --> 00:35:04,190
他们估计很快能恢复
They're expecting a quick recovery.

512
00:35:06,720 --> 00:35:09,320
你做得非常好  总统先生
You've done an outstanding job, Mr. President.

513
00:35:09,870 --> 00:35:13,280
-你也是  克莱尔  -我要去休息一会儿了
